otherFacts.name: Interior
otherFacts.value: One Living Area, Utility Room Inside, Separate Dining Room, Open Floor Plan, All Bedrooms Upstairs

data.description: This single family home is located in a quiet family neighborhood of Oak Bluff. The home features a large living area downstairs with separate dining that can also be used as office space etc. All 4 bedrooms are located upstairs along with 2 full baths. The home also features a wood deck and spacious shaded backyard with fire pit. Just 15 mins to Sea World or Six Flags, 10 mins to UTSA and minutes from some of the best shopping and dining in San Antonio. The home has renters in it and is a perfect money generating investment property. It is a successful long term rental, short term rental or your future family home.
